      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:38:10",
      "text": [
        " إِنَّ عَلِيّاً ( عليه السلام ) قَضَى فِي سِنِّ الصَّبِيِّ قَبْلَ أَنْ يَثَّغِرَ بَعِيراً بَعِيراً فِي كُلِّ سِنٍّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Muhammad Bin Al Hassan Bin Shamoun, from Abdullah Bin Abdul Rahman, from Misma’a, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has sad: ‘Ali<sup>asws</sup> judged regarding a tooth of a child before it extrudes, with a camel, a camel regarding each tooth’."
        ]
